      'Six at the top means:\rMissing the return.\rMisfortune.\rMisfortune from within and without.\rIf armies are set marching in this way,\rOne will in the end suffer a great defeat,\rDisastrous for the ruler of the country.\rFor ten years\rIt will not be possible to attack again.',
